{"data":[{"date":"07:56 06/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 6/7: Ronaldo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-67-ronaldo-gan-nhu-la-nguoi-cua-juve.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 6/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Messi mu\u1ed1n Pogba t\u1edbi Barcelona.</strong> Lionel Messi mu\u1ed1n Barcelona k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba t\u1eeb Manchester United. Sau khi b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 Antoine Griezmann m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u00fa \u00fd sang m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p kh\u00e1c. Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Paulinho khu trung tuy\u1ebfn Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ronaldo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve. </strong>Theo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Goal, Cristiano Ronaldo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus. CR7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A v\u1ec1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro/ m\u00f9a. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 khi\u1ebfn cho ph\u00eda Real Madrid b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi h\u1ecd mong ch\u1edd Ronaldo \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 67 Ronaldo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 67 Ronaldo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Mendes-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-Ronaldo-tai-Real-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00f3 tin Ronaldo chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Argentina mu\u1ed1n thay Sampaoli. </strong>C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Mario Kempes mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV Argentina n\u1ebfu&nbsp; Jorge Sampaoli b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i. Sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i, chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Sampaoli lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i d\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2022.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i gia mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Shaqiri. </strong>Manchester United s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri t\u1eeb Stoke City. Theo t\u1edd The Sun, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, ch\u00ednh c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Napoli m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho Jorginho t\u1edbi Man City. </strong>Napoli m\u1edbi c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Fabian Ruiz t\u1eeb Real Betis. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Napoli coi nh\u01b0 m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho t\u1edbi Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Jorginho\" title=\"tien ve Jorginho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/26/man-city-sap-co-jorginho-cua-napoli.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Jorginho r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda sang Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nBarca g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1edbi cho Willian.</strong> Barcelona \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1edbi cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Sau khi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m s\u1edf h\u1eefu tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Brazil th\u00f4ng qua con s\u1ed1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Tottenham v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Liverpol trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Grealish. </strong>Theo t\u1edd Mirror, Tottenham s\u1eafp gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool khi ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi anh.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nSouthgate v\u1eabn c\u1ea7m l\u00e1i Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2022.</strong> Ngay t\u1eeb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n HLV Gareth Southgate. Theo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Telegraph, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0a Tam s\u01b0 t\u1edbi VCK Euro 2020, Southgate s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng cho t\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 n\u0103m 2022.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4003","checkdouble":"190466"},{"date":"07:40 06/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh l\u00e0m l\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/nguoi-dai-dien-vo-tinh-lam-lo-tuong-lai-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jorge Mendes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo. \u201cSi\u00eau c\u00f2\u201d n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng n\u00e0y v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin CR7 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus chi \u0111\u1eadm cho Ronaldo</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (100 tri\u1ec7u Euro) t\u1edbi Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 33, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Los Blancos th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua 44 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 44 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n9 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i Real, Ronaldo c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu chinh ph\u1ee5c nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 4 Champions League v\u00e0 2 La Liga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mendes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mendes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Mendes-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-Ronaldo-tai-Real-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00f3 tin Ronaldo chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n nh\u1edb ngay sau khi Real \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League m\u00f9a 2017/18, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd, nghe \u0111\u00e2u c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Man United \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro/ m\u00f9a. Ch\u00ednh c\u1ef1u gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Luciano Moggi \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus-180-190431.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus</span>.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mendes v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJorge Mendes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo trong l\u00fac d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn s\u1ee5c s\u00f4i. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao n\u00e0y g\u1ee3i \u00fd v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. Qua \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec vi\u1ec7c Mendes x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Juventus trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jorge Mendes bi tinh nghi tron thue.\" title=\"Jorge Mendes b\u1ecb t\u00ecnh nghi tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/13/sau-cris-ronaldo-sieu-co-jorge-mendes-bi-dieu-tra-tron-thue.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mendes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea9n \u00fd</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;N\u1ebfu Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd m\u00e3i m\u00e3i bi\u1ebft \u01a1n CLB, ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean y t\u1ebf, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c Madridistas tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi&rdquo;, Mendes n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u1edd Record. &ldquo;M\u1ed9t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u1edbi v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Real t\u1eeb Man United n\u0103m 2009, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 450 b\u00e0n sau 438 tr\u1eadn cho h\u1ecd tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Anh \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eafm gi\u1eef k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus s\u1edbm m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Higuain</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/truyen-thong-chau-au-deu-khang-dinh-95-ronaldo-sang-juventus-180-190379.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 95% Ronaldo c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-24-de-che-siro-chua-the-sup-do-421-190218.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 24: \u0110\u1ebf ch\u1ebf &ldquo;Si-R\u00f4&rdquo; ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/an-tuong-world-cup/cristiano-ronaldo-cau-thu-co-tam-va-tai-471-190213.html\">B\u00e0i d\u1ef1 thi \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng World Cup: Cristiano Ronaldo - C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u00e2m v\u00e0 t\u00e0i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-va-messi-dat-tay-nhau-ve-nuoc-doan-ket-cuoc-hanh-trinh-421-190180.html\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi d\u1eaft tay nhau v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc: \u0110o\u1ea1n k\u1ebft cu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4002","checkdouble":"190465"},{"date":"08:42 06/07","title":"R\u1eddi Juventus sang Real Madrid, Ronaldo mang l\u1ed9c cho Man Utd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/5/roi-juventus-sang-real-madrid-ronaldo-mang-loc-cho-man-utd.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Manchester United v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Sporting Lisbon s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i hoa h\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n 2,5% trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus mua Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y: <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus-180-190431.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, CR7 s\u1ebd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Bernabeu, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 kh\u00f3 ai ng\u1edd t\u1edbi cho si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i 2,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro khi Juventus mua Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i 2,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro khi Juventus mua Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/roi-juventus-sang-real-madrid-ronaldo-mang-loc-cho-man-utd.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i 2,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro khi Juventus mua Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u00e0 Juventus, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p l\u1eafm ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a Paris Saint-Germain hay tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 x\u01b0a Manchester United. \u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester sau bao \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ee9a con c\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb c\u00e1c C\u0110V, ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 vui v\u1ebb v\u00ec nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf \u201ctr\u00ean tr\u1eddi r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, Man Utd s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i hoa h\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n 2,5% trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus mua Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 2,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro hay 2,2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea3 CLB kh\u1edfi nghi\u1ec7p Sporting Lisbon c\u1ee7a CR7 c\u0169ng h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 1,9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec trong b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2009, Man Utd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1eb1m h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Real Madrid b\u00e1n Ronaldo trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, nh\u01b0ng lu\u1eadt l\u1ec7 chung v\u1eabn cho ph\u00e9p h\u1ecd c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Sporting Lisbon \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng khi chia tay nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb do ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh Turin nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng ho\u00e0ng, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus-180-190431.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus</span> v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB gi\u00e0u th\u00e0nh t\u00edch nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-dai-dien-vo-tinh-lam-lo-tuong-lai-ronaldo-421-190465.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh l\u00e0m l\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/juventus-coi-nhu-trung-xo-so-neu-chieu-mo-duoc-ronaldo-184-190455.html\">Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo, Serie A coi nh\u01b0 tr\u00fang s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eafc</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus s\u1edbm m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Higuain</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4001","checkdouble":"190468"},{"date":"19:22 05/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 5/7: L\u00fd do Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-57-ly-do-ronaldo-muon-roi-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 5/7.</h2><h2>T\u1ea1i sao Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real?\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 57 L\u00fd do Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 57 L\u00fd do Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Moggi-tiet-lo-Ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 5/7: Ronaldo chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Marca kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Cristiano Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid b\u1edfi v\u00ec anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Bernabeu. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid ra gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 anh cho th\u1ea5y CR7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u00e0 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho th\u1ea5y Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus t\u1ea1i Serie A.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>PSG \u01b0u ti\u00ean chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kante</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Goal \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng PSG \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kante t\u1eeb Chelsea h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Tanguy Ndombele \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Kante n\u1ebfu m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Chelsea c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Kante. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, PSG c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c g\u00e1n Adrien Rabiot v\u00e0o nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pavard \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bayern</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Kicker kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Manchester United v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Benjamin Pavard t\u1eeb Stuttgart. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. Pavard \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia nh\u1eadp Bayern nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i \u1edf Stuttgart th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Allianz Arena v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2019.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Bailly ra y\u00eau s\u00e1ch v\u1edbi MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd The Sun cho bi\u1ebft trung v\u1ec7 Eric Bailly mu\u1ed1n th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1edbi Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford nh\u01b0ng lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Bailly hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Mourinho th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng anh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 15 tr\u1eadn cho MU.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Odriozola ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd AS \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Alvaro Odriozola \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid t\u1eeb Real Sociedad. Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng v\u1ecdt l\u00ean t\u1edbi 40 tri\u1ec7u euro sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n mang \u0111\u1ebfn Real sau khi nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-0507-mu-va-chelsea-no-bom-tan-cung-luc-184-190395.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 05/07: MU v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u1ed5 &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; c\u00f9ng l\u00fac</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-47-tony-kroos-ra-tuyen-bo-soc-sau-world-cup-2018-421-190377.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 4/7: Toni Kroos s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0a ra tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ed1c sau World Cup 2018?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4000","checkdouble":"190452"},{"date":"21:19 05/07","title":"Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo, Serie A coi nh\u01b0 tr\u00fang s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eafc","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/5/juventus-coi-nhu-trung-xo-so-neu-chieu-mo-duoc-ronaldo.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Christian Vieri m\u1edbi l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Ronaldo coi nh\u01b0 gi\u00fap cho Serie A tr\u00fang v\u00e9 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eafc v\u00ec l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 theo d\u00f5i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u0103ng v\u1ecdt.</h2><h2>Cristiano Ronaldo ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Juventus?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Real Madrid trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y r\u1ea5t \u00edt quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Italia \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y qua v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho CR7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo, Serie A coi nh\u01b0 tr\u00fang s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eafc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo, Serie A coi nh\u01b0 tr\u00fang s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eafc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/juventus-coi-nhu-trung-xo-so-neu-chieu-mo-duoc-ronaldo.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Juventus s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Goal ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1edd anh t\u1edbi k\u00fd t\u1ea1i Turin. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus-180-190431.html\" target=\"_blank\">si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Juventus</span>, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Vieri \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 vui m\u1eebng t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cV\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 tr\u00fang v\u00e9 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eafc. Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i \u00edt n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea3i Serie A. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng si\u00eau sao kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. Nh\u01b0ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Serie A h\u1ed3i sinh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cK\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch h\u01a1n khi theo d\u00f5i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. M\u1ed7i cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i t\u1ef1 h\u1ecfi Juventus thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u00e0 Ronaldo th\u00ec ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao nhi\u00eau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac Ronaldo ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea3ng tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb CR7 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi \u0111\u00e3 chinh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u t\u1ea1i Manchester United v\u00e0 Real Madrid, ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Ronaldo nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c, n\u00f3 s\u1ebd k\u00edch n\u1ed5 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Real Madrid c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn Ronaldo:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-57-ly-do-ronaldo-muon-roi-real-184-190452.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 5/7: L\u00fd do Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus-180-190431.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3999","checkdouble":"190455"},{"date":"22:36 05/07","title":"Forsberg ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Premier League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/liverpool-va-arsenal-khong-nen-chieu-mo-forsberg.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Johan Mjallby cho r\u1eb1ng Emil Forsberg ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Premier League cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 MU, Arsenal hay Liverpool.</h2><h2>Forsberg li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Premier League</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea1i gia Premier League. Trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o RB Leipzig.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Forsberg ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Forsberg ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Forsberg-chua-du-trinh-da-o-Premier-League-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mjallby cho r\u1eb1ng Emil Forsberg ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nForsberg c\u0169ng\u00a0 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t C\u0110V c\u1ee7a s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Premier League. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Man United trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> k\u1ebft th\u00fac. B\u1edfi ng\u00f4i sao mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Nga v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<h2>Mjallby ho\u00e0i nghi v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Forsberg</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Johan Mjallby, chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf Premier League l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i h\u01a1i qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Forsberg l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean t\u1edd BetStars tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 Anh, c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Celtic cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cEmil Forsberg l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111ang d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i Bundesliga. Nh\u01b0ng 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i Anh l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eadp trung nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. S\u1ebd r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu Forsberg \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i top 4 Premier League l\u00fac n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T\u00a0Th\u1ee5y\u00a0\u0110i\u1ec3n:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-thuy-dien-se-lam-cho-dt-anh-phai-cam-nin-469-190454.html\">Ibrahimovic: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd l\u00e0m cho \u0110T Anh ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2m n\u00edn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/granqvist-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-thuy-dien-vs-anh-421-190391.html\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3998","checkdouble":"190458"},{"date":"06:06 06/07","title":"C\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Wilshere ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf \u1edf CLB Premier League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/18/wilshere-kiem-tra-y-te-tai-west-ham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Wilshere ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i West Ham tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c CLB r\u1eb1ng n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u00eda sau.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Wilshere chia tay Arsenal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Jack Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 do. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal sau bu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery. Chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Wilshere s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n b\u1edfi Mesut Ozil t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 2018/19 tr\u1edf \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong kho\u1ea3ng 1 n\u0103m qua, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Ozil c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n t\u00e1n kh\u00f4ng \u00edt. \u0110\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, anh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Arsenal l\u00e2u d\u00e0i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Wilshere, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u00ean mi\u00ean trong th\u1eddi gian qua b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wilshere ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i West Ham tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Wilshere ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i West Ham tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/18/Wilshere-kiem-tra-y-te-tai-West-Ham-truoc-khi-chuyen-nhuong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Wilshere chia tay Arsenal sau m\u00f9a 2017/18</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nWilshere t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh v\u00e0 ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Arsenal t\u1eeb n\u0103m 16 tu\u1ed5i. Nh\u01b0ng phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f4i khi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m h\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng n\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfp nhau \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1edd s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u0111ang ch\u1eefng l\u1ea1i tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i West Ham</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong h\u00f4m nay, Wilshere ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i West Ham tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh London v\u1edbi Arsenal \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed5 sung anh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch Premier League 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Wilshere tro lai DT Anh sau nhung man trinh dien tot o CLB\" title=\"Jack Wilshere tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t \u1edf CLB\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/wilshere-kiem-tra-y-te-tai-west-ham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Wilshere ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i West Ham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Manuel Pellegrini \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t m\u1ebfn m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Wilshere v\u00e0 th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c West Ham \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Nh\u01b0ng Wilshere tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u00e1c b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf chi ti\u1ebft t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh The Hammers.<br>\r\n\u00a0<br>\r\nWest Ham s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1edf kh\u00e2u n\u00e0y v\u00ec mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng Wilshere \u0111ang trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n 39 l\u1ea7n trong 4 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i Premier League cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7, th\u00eam 27 l\u1ea7n cho Bournemouth m\u00f9a 2016/17 d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Jack Wilshere tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/santi-cazorla-co-vai-loi-muon-gui-toi-jack-wilshere-172-189052.html\">Santi Cazorla c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi t\u1edbi Jack Wilshere</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wilshere-chinh-thuc-roi-arsenal-172-188988.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Wilshere tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eddi Arsenal ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wilshere-se-chot-tuong-lai-sau-cuoc-gap-hlv-emery-172-188179.html\">Wilshere s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sau cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p HLV Emery</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-muon-mua-dennis-praet-cua-sampdoria-172-187155.html\">Arsenal nh\u1eafm sao Serie A thay Wilshere</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3997","checkdouble":"190460"},{"date":"13:55 05/07","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 4-1 U19 L\u00e0o (KT): Tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-lao-15h30-ngay-57.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm U19 L\u00e0o \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Indonesia.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2>T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P: U19 VI\u1ec6T NAM 4-1 U19 L\u00c0O\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/5/U19-Viet-Nam-4-1-U19-Lao.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nTR\u1eacN \u0110\u1ea4U B\u1eaeT \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HI\u1ec6P 1</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Ph\u00fat 5: V\u00e0i ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam - nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eb7c \u00e1o tr\u1eafng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ph\u00fat 15: S\u1ee9c \u00e9p \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng. To\u00e0n b\u1ed9 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ee7a U19 L\u00e0o \u0111\u00e3 l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ph\u00fat 18: R\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m. V\u1eeba r\u1ed3i l\u00e0 c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng, nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i \u0111i \u0111\u00fang v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 0-0.<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/5/U19-Viet-Nam-phut-18.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Ph\u00fat 25: <strong>V\u00c0OOO! </strong>Xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng leo bi\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Danh Trung \u0111\u00e3 \u1eadp v\u00e0o r\u1ea5t nhanh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/5/U19-Viet-Nam-phut-25.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ph\u00fat 35: \u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc! U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh, v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i l\u00e0 pha b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/5/U19-Viet-Nam-phut-35.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Ph\u00fat 36: Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa tung pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1. U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Ph\u00fat 38: <strong>T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 2-0!</strong> T\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n l\u00e0 L\u00ea Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t su\u00f4n s\u1ebb cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00e1o tr\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/5/U19-Viet-Nam-phut-38.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Ph\u00fat 45+2: <strong>V\u00c0OOO!</strong> T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 3-0 cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00e1o tr\u1eafng, v\u1eabn t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u quen thu\u1ed9c. U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, trong khi U19 L\u00e0o v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/5/U19-Viet-Nam-phut-47.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<strong>HI\u1ec6P 2&nbsp;</strong> - Ph\u00fat 46: Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 cho hi\u1ec7p 2 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1eb7c \u00e1o tr\u1eafng s\u1ebd b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ph\u00fat 55: T\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, U19 L\u00e0o \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ed3n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Ph\u00fat 64: C\u00f3 x\u00f4 x\u00e1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ra chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng cho 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ed9t l\u00fac. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 15 H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 23 Duy Ki\u00ean. C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c gi\u1eef b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/5/U19-Viet-Nam-phut-64.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Ph\u00fat 70: R\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc, su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 4, sau khi b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a L\u00e0o. \u00cdt ph\u00fat v\u1eeba qua, L\u00e0o v\u1eabn \u0111ang nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, trong khi Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u1ea3m nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/5/U19-Viet-Nam-phut-70.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ph\u00fat 75: <strong>V\u00c0O! </strong>T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 tung c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eb7t, kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh L\u00e0o b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u1ea3. T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 4-0 cho U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/5/U19-Viet-Nam-phut-75.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Ph\u00fat 86: V\u1eeba r\u1ed3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng 2 \u0111\u00e1nh 1, nh\u01b0ng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e1 ngon \u0103n n\u00e0y, khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ph\u00fat 90: <strong>T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00fat ng\u1eafn! </strong>Trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, U19 L\u00e0o \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh. T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 1-4. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/5/U19-Viet-Nam-phut-90.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0o \u0111\u00e3 thua c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 Indonesia, ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng 4 l\u1ea7n. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e9p t\u00ednh b\u1eafc c\u1ea7u, c\u00f3 logic cao nh\u01b0ng \u1edf ch\u1eebng m\u1ef1c n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp ngang h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 Indonesia trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh 2 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng A. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHai th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a L\u00e0o \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi L\u00e0o. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf cho th\u1ea5y, L\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. Trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u1ebb l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng ch\u01b0a g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho c\u00e1c th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u00f9ng trang l\u1ee9a c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 L\u00e0o 15h30 chi\u1ec1u h\u00f4m nay 57 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 L\u00e0o 15h30 chi\u1ec1u h\u00f4m nay 57 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-572018.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u1ebb Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ecf ra ch\u1ee7 quan, xem th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. M\u1ed9t th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac, bi\u1ebft t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ngay th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1eafng l\u1edbn v\u00e0 th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 cho Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y, \u0111\u00edch nh\u1eafm c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u L\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm. B\u1edfi th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf so s\u00e1nh n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd, b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec7m t\u1ed1t cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 7/7. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, b\u1edfi vi\u1ec7c s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ed7 m\u00e1y c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ee5c tr\u1eb7c trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n<br>\r\nU19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: T\u00f9ng L\u00e2m, V\u0103n Nam, Thi\u00ean \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n T\u1edbi, V\u0103n C\u00f4ng, Vi\u1ec7t Anh, H\u1ed3ng S\u01a1n, B\u1ea3o To\u00e0n, M\u1ea1nh D\u0169ng, V\u0103n Xu\u00e2n, H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng. <br>\r\nU19 L\u00e0o: Venvongsot, Singsavang, Champathong, Phomvongsa, Sinonalath, Thinolath, Nilan, Buonkong, Xayxanapanya, Thongsavath, Khamsouliya. <br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3996","checkdouble":"190419"},{"date":"14:10 05/07","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam 10-0 N\u1eef Singapore (16h00 ng\u00e0y 5/7)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-singapore-16h00-ngay-57.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Singapore: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Singapore gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 5/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)\r\n<h2><br />\r\nLINK XEM TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP N\u1eee VI\u1ec6T NAM VS N\u1eee SINGAPORE</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rJsUGoN9doA\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> \u0110a s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Myanmar, \u0111\u1ec1u \u201cd\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01a1\u201d.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng minh trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 Indonesia t\u1edbi 6-0. Singapore th\u00ec khi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Indonesia, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chia \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-0 n\u00ean ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o cho th\u1ea5y, s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/dt-nuvn-singapore.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nKh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 khi cho r\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u201cc\u1eef d\u01b0\u1ee3t\u201d m\u00e0 HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ea7n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi, \u00edt ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng cao kinh nghi\u1ec7m, t\u00edch l\u0169y chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. S\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu BHL Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u00a0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1. Nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0o \u0111i ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa, Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3995","checkdouble":"190420"},{"date":"17:14 05/07","title":"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/3/u23-viet-nam-nam-chung-bang-voi-nhat-ban-tai-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 khi c\u00f9ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ph\u00e2n b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam v\u00e0 n\u1eef t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra. L\u00e1 th\u0103m \u0111\u01b0a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 U23 Pakistan v\u00e0 U23 Nepan - hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/U23-Viet-Nam-nam-chung-bang-voi-Nhat-Ban-tai-ASIAD-2018-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nASIAD 2018 c\u00f3 24 \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 chia th\u00e0nh 6 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, 4 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb 14/8 \u0111\u1ebfn 1/9 t\u1ea1i Indonesia. C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 v\u00e0 th\u00eam 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i h\u01a1n. Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 th\u1edf v\u1edbi HongKong, L\u00e0o v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0i Loan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng C v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0110T n\u1eef Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan. \u0110\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng C.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:\u00a0</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng A:</strong> Indonesia, H\u1ed3ng K\u00f4ng, L\u00e0o, \u0110\u00e0i B\u1eafc Trung Hoa</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng B:</strong> Th\u00e1i Lan, Uzbekistan, Bangladesh, Qatar</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng C:</strong> Iraq, Trung Qu\u1ed1c, Timor Leste, Syria</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng D: </strong>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Pakistan, Nepal</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng E:</strong> H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Kyrgyzstan, Malaysia, Bahrain</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng F:</strong> CHDCND Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean, Saudi Arabia, Iran, Myanmar</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:\u00a0</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng A:</strong> Indonesia, Maldives, \u0110\u00e0i B\u1eafc Trung Hoa, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng B:</strong> Tajikistan, H\u1ed3ng K\u00f4ng, Trung Qu\u1ed1c, CHDCND Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng C:</strong> Th\u00e1i Lan, Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-dung-toan-doi-thu-dang-gom-truoc-asiad-2018-168-190369.html\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee5ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu-168-189826.html\">Gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/kem-mieng-u23-viet-nam-bong-da-thai-lan-gap-rut-chuan-bi-cho-asiad-168-188833.html\">K\u00e9m mi\u1ebfng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-dt-han-quoc-can-su-gia-do-park-hang-seo-de-tao-dia-chan-o-world-cup-421-188831.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u1ea7n \u2018s\u1ef1 gi\u00e0 d\u01a1\u2019 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/xuan-truong-tiec-vi-khong-duoc-di-xem-world-cup-2018-465-188289.html\">Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i xem World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/dtqg/hlv-park-hang-seo-mong-cac-cau-thu-u23-viet-nam-duoc-bao-ve-292-188283.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo: C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3994","checkdouble":"190436"},{"date":"12:15 05/07","title":"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup, sao Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU quan t\u00e2m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/4/toa-sang-tai-world-cup-mina-duoc-mu-quan-tam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man United \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 24 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u1eb1m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca sau m\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>MU nh\u1eafm Yerry Mina</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u00fa \u00fd t\u1edbi m\u00ecnh khi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cho Colombia \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>. \u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 Colombia \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi theo d\u00f5i nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Mina t\u1ea1i World Cup, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. <strong>Man United \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 24 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mina. </strong>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester c\u00f3 v\u1ebb r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y khi m\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu.</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Barca\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup, Mina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU quan t\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup, Mina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU quan t\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/toa-sang-tai-world-cup-mina-duoc-mu-quan-tam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU quan t\u00e2m sau m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalanonia c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t vi\u00ean ng\u1ecdc s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 Yerry Mina. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 Barca kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 trao cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 Mina ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u0169ng c\u1edfi m\u1edf v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00e8m th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua l\u1ea1i trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n n\u1eefa gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai tu\u1ea7n sau. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 bu\u1ed5i g\u1eb7p m\u1eb7t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra hay kh\u00f4ng. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Man United, Yerry Mina ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford trong v\u00f2ng 1 tu\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Yerry Mina ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n cho Barca. Anh c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 6 l\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf La Liga c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 C\u00fap nh\u00e0 Vua. T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Mina l\u00e0 377 v\u1edbi 4 l\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u1edf hai \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00f3i tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fabinho-khang-dinh-chua-tung-tien-gan-mu-172-190409.html\">Fabinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ee5t v\u1edbi MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-vuot-mat-con-moi-vi-real-madrid-172-190411.html\">Chelsea vu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t con m\u1ed3i v\u00ec... Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3993","checkdouble":"190414"},{"date":"16:23 05/07","title":"Barca ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au tr\u00ean TTCN","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/6/barca-tiep-tuc-nhan-don-dau-tren-ttcn.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, CLB Sevilla t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Lenglet cho Barcelona.\r\n</h2><h2>Barca ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh trung v\u1ec7 Clement Lenglet l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p r\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, 35 tri\u1ec7u euro ti\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1 &ldquo;k\u1ef3 k\u00e8o&rdquo; v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Barca g\u1ee3i \u00fd Sevilla v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 35 tri\u1ec7u euro, nh\u01b0ng hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3&hellip; th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ee3t (tr\u1ea3 g\u00f3p). \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u00eau b\u00e0i quen thu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a Barca tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a Lenglet \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, G\u0110TT c\u1ee7a Sevilla &ndash; \u00f4ng Joaquin Caparros cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang ta h\u00e3y l\u00e0m r\u00f5 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lenglet.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Barca mu\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng Sevilla kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n. S\u1ebd l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1c n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, khi \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i. C\u00f2n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n? Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sevilla t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Lenglet cho Barcelona\" title=\"trung ve Clement Lenglet\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/barca-tiep-tuc-nhan-don-dau-tren-ttcn.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sevilla t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Lenglet cho Barcelona</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Hi\u1ec7n nay, Clement Lenglet l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eeba m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, v\u00e0 \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. S\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0o v\u1edbi Barca&rdquo; &ndash; Sevilla t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Clement Lenglet, n\u0103m nay 23 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sevilla chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb Nancy v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 3,5 tri\u1ec7u euro th\u00e1ng Gi\u00eang n\u0103m 2017. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Sanchez Pizjuan \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2021, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Barca, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u con m\u1ed3i l\u1edbn tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, b\u1edfi c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m \u0103n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Antoine Griezmann c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou, b\u1edfi Barca&hellip; kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 100 tri\u1ec7u euro tr\u1ea3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i Atletico cho tr\u1ea3 g\u00f3p. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a 2 bom t\u1ea5n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp m\u00e0 Barca k\u00edch n\u1ed5 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i &ndash; Dembele v\u00e0 Coutinho.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c CLB Sevilla t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Lenglet cho Barcelona, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ho\u1eb7c s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro, ho\u1eb7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/willian-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-duoc-barca-quan-tam-421-190386.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/11/willian-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-duoc-barca-quan-tam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/willian-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-duoc-barca-quan-tam-421-190386.html\">Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca quan t\u00e2m</span><br>\r\nWillian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Camp Nou.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-barca-172-190353.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/12/18/arsenal-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-barca-172-190353.html\">Arsenal b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Barca</span><br>\r\nArsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Andre Gomes n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, HLV Unai Emery nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha thay v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Jack Wilshere \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3992","checkdouble":"190407"},{"date":"16:18 05/07","title":"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/5/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb c\u1ef1u gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia, Luciano Moggi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 CR7 \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf xong xu\u00f4i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd t\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A, Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro d\u00e0nh cho Cristiano Ronaldo. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 33, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1eabn ghi t\u1edbi 44 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Real Madrid \u1edf m\u00f9a 2017/18, c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n, trong 9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Ronaldo lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Madrid. V\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Champions League \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, Juventus r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a CR7. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juve s\u1edbm m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Higuain</span> t\u1ea1i CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Moggi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Moggi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Moggi-tiet-lo-Ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Juventus chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLuciano Moggi t\u1eebng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Juventus t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2006. Trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, d\u1ef1a theo ngu\u1ed3n tin m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, \u00f4ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u1edbi Juventus t\u1ea1i Munich\u201d, Moggi n\u00f3i tr\u00ean k\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Italia, Tele7Gold. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 trong \u0111\u1ea7u sau khi n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt quan tr\u1ecdng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1eebng \u201cv\u1ed3 h\u1ee5t\u201d Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Moggi t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n Ronaldo tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Juventus n\u0103m 2002. Khi \u0111\u00f3, Ronaldo v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Sporting Lisbon song \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo chuan bi chuyen toi Juventus\" title=\"Ronaldo chuan bi chuyen toi Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Moggi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMoggi t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 Marcelo Salas di chuy\u1ec3n theo h\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i song b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh. Sau \u0111\u00f3, CR7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Manchester United v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2003. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean\u201d, c\u1ef1u gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Juve n\u00f3i. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1edbi quan s\u00e1t c\u1eadu \u1ea5y thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi m\u1edbi 18 tu\u1ed5i song \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 ch\u1eefng ch\u1ea1c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng may, Marcelo Salas \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Sporting Lisbon v\u00ec mu\u1ed1n quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i River Plate. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ea3 th\u00eam 5 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i, nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-va-messi-dat-tay-nhau-ve-nuoc-doan-ket-cuoc-hanh-trinh-421-190180.html\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi d\u1eaft tay nhau v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc: \u0110o\u1ea1n k\u1ebft cu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-la-messi-la-ronaldo-cua-dt-anh-421-190088.html\">Harry Kane l\u00e0 Messi, l\u00e0 Ronaldo c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-sau-tran-thua-cua-dt-bo-dao-nha-465-190053.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thua-uruguay-hlv-bo-dao-nha-xin-ronaldo-mot-dieu-421-190047.html\">Thua Uruguay, HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha xin Ronaldo m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3991","checkdouble":"190431"}]}